race.description: Goulburn Australia Country Boosted Mdn Hcp
race.comment: ENTIRELY OAK (3) comes here deep into the prep and won't find an easier race to shed his Maiden status. Shouldered the 59kg with a fading fourth over 1200m at Nowra. No excuses back to the 1100m. MIDNIGHT MOOSE (2) Knight Exemplar entire from Jhuldi on debut for the Rob Potter yard. Fitted with a sharp trial win over 950m at Cowra. Gets every chance from the draw. AIRFIELD (4) lightly raced gelding who resumes with a string of minor placings. Failed to handle the heavy (8) track when fifth over 1100m at Nowra. Back without a trial and can get off the mark today. CHERRY JUBILEE (7) returns from a lengthy spell. Came to the end of her campaign with a tiring eighth over 1200m at Wagga. Back without a trial and can sneak into the minor money with the claim.
